      "description": "<div class=\"no-overflow\"><div class=\"section\" id=\"additional-resources\">\n    <h2><i class=\"fa fa-plus-circle\"></i> Go Further!</h2>\n    <h4>Additional Resources</h4>\n    <p>For those eager to expand their knowledge beyond the core content, this section offers additional resources. Here, you'll find links to further readings, advanced topics, and supplemental materials that can enrich your learning experience.</p>\n    <ol><li>Ashish Kumar. (2019). Mastering Pandas : A Complete Guide to Pandas, From Installation to Advanced Data Analysis Techniques, 2nd Edition. Packt Publishing.</li><li>Theodore Petrou. (2017). Pandas Cookbook : Publisher’s Note: A New Second Edition, Updated Completely for Pandas 1.x with Additional Chapters, Has Now Been Published. This Edition From 2017 Is Outdated and Is Based on Pandas 0.20. Packt Publishing.</li></ol><ul>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>",
